      <aside class="text-center w-32 top-0 sticky">
        <nav class="bg-slate-900 font-bold flex flex-col h-min -mt-2 p-6 top-0 sticky shadow-lg shadow-gray-900 md:flex-row md:h-16 md:w-screen md:-mt-0">
          <h1 class="text-purple-500 text-xl mb-6 self-center md:inline-flex md:mb-0 md:mr-6">Wolfie's Space</h1>
          <a class="self-center" href="#">
            <div class="bg-slate-700 h-12 w-32 md:h-16">
              <p class="pt-3 md:pt-5">Home</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a class="self-center" href="#">
            <div class="h-12 w-32 hover:bg-slate-700 hover:duration-[250ms] md:h-16">
              <p class="pt-3 md:pt-5">About</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a class="self-center" href="#">
            <div class="h-12 w-32 hover:bg-slate-700 hover:duration-[250ms] md:h-16">
              <p class="pt-3 md:pt-5">Projects</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a class="self-center" href="#">
            <div class="h-12 w-32 hover:bg-slate-700 hover:duration-[250ms] md:h-16">
              <p class="pt-3 md:pt-5">Contact</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </nav>
      </aside>

      <div id="post-container" class="w-2/3 mr-11 ml-11 self-center md:ml-0 md:mr-0">
        <div class="bg-slate-700 text-center flex-col mt-6 px-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-purple-500 shadow-lg shadow-gray-900">
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold pt-6">Welcome to Wolfie's Space!</h1>
          <hr class="bg-slate-800 h-px mt-6 mb-1 border-0"/>
          <h2 class="text-xl -mb-3.5">A deep-dive into questions such as "Why do I do this to myself?"</h2>
          <hr class="bg-slate-800 h-px mt-6 mb-1 border-0"/>
          <p class="pb-1 -mb-4">
            This is my personal website, it is and probably forever will be under construction.
            I'll continually update it as my projects change and my skills improve. As of now these
            posts are created manually and the other pages don't exist, that will change - eventually.
          </p>
          <hr class="bg-slate-800 h-px mt-6 mb-1 border-0"/>
          <p class="pb-2 text-xs">Post by Ayla - 11/22/2022 - 12:17AM - Thanks for visiting!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
